description: If being in love to the right or the left wasn’t crazy enough for you then here are some Japanese emoticons that not only are in love, but they’re facing forward too! They must be looking straight at the person or thing that they love. If you send this to a friend, it might look like you are in love with them! Either that or the chocolate cake you’re thinking about… Mmmm..
